message.raw:
Tabs are now dynamically generated from the H5 file (and a device list)

Fixed a bunch of bugs with acquisition on the ni_pcie_6363.
Bugs related to:
acquisition of only 1 channel (array sizes)
sample per channel being set to a float when rate was less than 1000 (now set to int)
